note right of reservation501
This snapshot models the state produced by
OnlineBookingServiceImpl#createOnlineReservation():
1. create Reservation with type ONLINE
2. save ReservationTableMapping rows
3. soft-lock selected tables
4. move Reservation to PENDING_PAYMENT
end note

note bottom of table08
OCCUPIED here means the table is soft-locked
for payment protection, not that the guest
has already checked in.
end note

note bottom of table09
If confirmPayment() succeeds later:
- reservation status becomes RESERVED
- softLockUntil becomes null
- lockedByReservationId becomes null
- table status becomes AVAILABLE again
end note

@enduml
